Package: sentimentcalculator
Type: Package
Title: A package for analyzing the true meaning of a text
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Isabelle", "Eliasson",
                  email = "isabelle.eliasson@ki.se",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package helps determine whether the sentiment of a text is positive, negative or neutral by analyzing keyword sentiment. The functions are designed to be used in the following order: format_text -> sentiment_counts -> sentiment_results. This package uses the SnowballC package for word stemming.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    SnowballC
